{"tid":2320002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子住酒店現金被掉包 假幣印「中國魔法銀行」","createTime":"2020-12-10T12:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:44:29.000Z","uid":343294,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"27fb7b1d2010d5a760ffd9794fcfa9a0c0e1c82f","tid":2320002,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"2020年12月06日18:30<br />\n<br />\n近日，張先生到北京出差，因要還借款，入住酒店時帶了10多萬的現金。還錢時，張先生髮現現金中竟然出現了50多張印著「中國魔法銀行」的假幣。民警調查發現，服務員王某趁著張先生離開，進了房間，剛掉包完假幣，就被張先生撞了個正著。隨後民警在服務員王某的宿舍起獲大量假幣。目前，王某因涉嫌盜竊罪被刑事拘留。<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/12/9DA5E7998ABCCDBD850B2050E04FC58A8DBAC31B_w569_h320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F12%2F9DA5E7998ABCCDBD850B2050E04FC58A8DBAC31B_w569_h320.jpg&h=511a8be8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/12/8A4C3D6E8A757BEE54916D4A4E1F02BB1A7BCF02_w561_h316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F12%2F8A4C3D6E8A757BEE54916D4A4E1F02BB1A7BCF02_w561_h316.jpg&h=e6c78264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a9404690acf30210cf7b49f8e68d9e3cd91b674","tid":2320002,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張先生髮現現金中竟然出現了50多張印著「中國魔法銀行」的假幣。</blockquote><br />\n喺頭髪發現?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df301076b7b98c0afda0dab27e096b372d9c37","tid":2320002,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張先生<span class=\"red\">髮現</span>現金中竟然出現了50多張印著「中國魔法銀行」的假幣。</blockquote><br />\n喺頭髪發現?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"586be175e9ad604db560c4baf516f9ce5880fa23","tid":2320002,"uid":143241,"like":0,"disli